{
  "stem": "979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- yeah-- part of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then we went-- they-- they put me to work, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to play the accordion with my brother's band there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Nazis were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were Nazis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Greek-- it was a Greek place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, if-- if they knew you were-- you were Jewish-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] he says, you-- you don't know what would happen, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because already the Greeks knew what's gonna happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but nobody knows-- knew we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got a good, you know, we got a good job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we were having a little money, you know-- enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then a year had passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly, we realized that the Nazis, they gave us to wear the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to the Jewish community, and they-- they took all our names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, in France, in Europe, they didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They do-- they did try to find the Jewish peoples, but nobody knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some went to the camp, some didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But with us, the community gave all our names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went to take the names from the community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know who gave them the name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they forced them, probably to give the names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they knew where everybody was living, and they decided to have ghettos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these ghettos were outside-- see, where-- like I lived near the ocean and all this-- we had to move out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to go to a district which was a poor district.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to call it the number 151.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the name of that district.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and there, we had to share a small little house with someone else and that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had special ghettos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So many would go here.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
